HAI 1.4
    HOW IZ I factorial YR n
        I HAS A prod ITZ 1
        I HAS A i ITZ 0
        IM IN YR loop UPPIN YR i TIL BOTH SAEM i AN n
            prod R PRODUKT OF prod AN SUM OF i AN 1
        IM OUTTA YR loop
        FOUND YR prod
    IF U SAY SO

    VISIBLE "5! = " AN I IZ factorial YR 5 MKAY
    VISIBLE "10! = " AN I IZ factorial YR 10 MKAY
KTHXBYE
